


Cac buoc tao 1 pull request

B1 Fork tren github de tao ban sao cua repo chung ve github ca nhan (repo ca nhan)
B2 Lay code tu github ve may tinh ca nhan bang lenh: git clone [remote URL]
luu y remote URL duoc lay o github ca nhan sau kho da fork
B3 Add remote (tao ket noi giua local va repo chung) bang lenh: git remote add [ten remote] [remote URL]
Luu y remote URL o day la link duoc lay o github ban dau(repo chung)





B4 tao nhanh moi
truoc khi tao nhanh moi can kiem tra nhanh dang dung bang lenh: git branch
neu dang o nhanh main thi moi co the tao ra nhanh moi bang lenh: git checkout -b [ten nhanh]
B5 thuc hien viec tao files coding tren thu muc vua clone
B6 add cac file vua tao bang lenh git add -A hoac git add .
B7 tao commit bang lenh git commit -m [ten conmit]
B8 day pull bang lenh git push origin [ten nhanh]
